---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Spatial Gnomics">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/applications/">Applications</a> / Spatial Gnomics</div>
      <h1>Spatial Gnomics</h1>
      <p>Resolve the spatial distribution of gnome gene expression within tissue sections.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section>
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="cards mb-2">
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🗺️</div><h3>SpatialGnome HD</h3><p>Sub-micron resolution spatial transcriptomics for gnome tissue sections.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🔵</div><h3>Visium Gnome</h3><p>Spot-based spatial gene expression profiling across the gnome transcriptome.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🧩</div><h3>Single-cell Gnomics</h3><p>Single-cell resolution spatial mapping of gnome cell populations.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📸</div><h3>Imaging Integration</h3><p>Co-registration of gnome expression data with histological imaging.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-info">
        Ready to start a spatial gnomics project? <a href="/platform/">Access the platform →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
